{"word":"H1696 - דָבַר - dâbar - daw-bar' - Answer","slug":"H1696","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">דָבַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>dâbar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>daw-bar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Answer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05D1;&#x05E8; - da&#x0302;bar</b> - <i>daw-bar'</i><p/>A primitive root; perhaps properly to <i>arrange</i>; but used figuratively (of words) to <i>speak</i>; rarely (in a destructive sense) to <i>subdue: - </i>answer, appoint, bid, command, commune, declare, destroy, give, name, promise, pronounce, rehearse, say, speak, be spokesman, subdue, talk, teach, tell, think, use [entreaties], utter, X well, X work."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1682\">H1682</a>, <a href=\"#/H1683\">H1683</a>, <a href=\"#/H1687\">H1687</a>, <a href=\"#/H1688\">H1688</a>, <a href=\"#/H1697\">H1697</a>, <a href=\"#/H1698\">H1698</a>, <a href=\"#/H1699\">H1699</a>, <a href=\"#/H1700\">H1700</a>, <a href=\"#/H1702\">H1702</a>, <a href=\"#/H1703\">H1703</a>, <a href=\"#/H1704\">H1704</a>, <a href=\"#/H1705\">H1705</a>, <a href=\"#/H4057\">H4057</a>"}]}